{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be artistic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Audio Network</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #A52A2A; /* Brownish Red */\n            --secondary-color: #D2B48C; /* Tan */\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a;\n            --text-color: #f0f0f0;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.8));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x700/A52A2A/FFFFFF?text=Crimson+Audio') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 70vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            z-index: 1;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            z-index: 1;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .section h3 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item {\n            background-color: #282828;\n            border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: left;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(165,42,42,0.4);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item h4 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item .listen-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item .listen-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #111;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            border-top: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            #hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.2em;\n            }\n            #hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            .section h3 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Crimson Audio Network</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n            <a href=\"#podcasts\">Podcasts</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Stories in Crimson</h2>\n        <p>Dive into a world of captivating narratives and insightful discussions, brought to you by the Crimson Audio Network.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>About Us</h3>\n            <p>Crimson Audio Network is a collective of passionate storytellers and thinkers, dedicated to producing high-quality audio content that sparks curiosity and fosters connection. We believe in the power of sound to transport, inform, and inspire.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"podcasts\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Our Podcasts</h3>\n            <div class=\"podcast-grid\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/280x200/A52A2A/FFFFFF?text=Crimson+Chronicles\" alt=\"Crimson Chronicles Cover\">\n                    <h4>Crimson Chronicles</h4>\n                    <p>Unearthing forgotten histories and the untold stories that shaped our world.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"listen-button\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/280x200/A52A2A/FFFFFF?text=Crimson+Conversations\" alt=\"Crimson Conversations Cover\">\n                    <h4>Crimson Conversations</h4>\n                    <p>Engaging dialogues with innovators, artists, and thought leaders.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"listen-button\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/280x200/A52A2A/FFFFFF?text=Crimson+Culture\" alt=\"Crimson Culture Cover\">\n                    <h4>Crimson Culture</h4>\n                    <p>Exploring the vibrant tapestry of art, music, and modern society.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"listen-button\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Get In Touch</h3>\n            <p>Have a story to share or a collaboration idea? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n            <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@crimsonaudio.com\">info@crimsonaudio.com</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Audio Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Crafted with passion and <a href=\"#hero\" style=\"color: var(--secondary-color);\">Crimson</a>.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}